<title>yạlly fy ḥmạk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yạlly fy ḥmạk ạ̉nạ qlby ʿạysẖ yạlly fy smạk mḥfwẓ mkạny
 wʿly̱ kfk ṣwrty nạqsẖ ( ạ̉nt yswʿ ạlly fdạny )2
 ạlqrạr - hllwyạ hllwyạ kl ḥyạty lyk bạhdyk
 hllwyạ hllwyạ bạsbḥk yạ ạ̉gẖly̱ mlyk
 2- nṣrty fyk rby ạ̉kydh mạsẖy mʿạyạ yạ rạʿy
 ḍmnt ly ḥyạẗ mjydẗ ( ṭwl rḥlty mạsk ạ̹ydy )2</lyrics>
</song>